{"tid":1553941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵既死穴係。。。。。","createTime":"2019-09-08T19:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T19:38:15.000Z","uid":283919,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff237cee185b9c452c40d1a021dd3dfadca3892c","tid":1553941,"uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:01:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">大家要攪清楚！</span></span><br />\n黨鐵既死穴並唔係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">鐵路收益</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n係黎自地產發展，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">賣樓先係佢最大收入來源</span></span>，一個盤分分鐘執百幾二百億，好似依家同鄉黑新地賣緊既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">匯璽</span></span>，佢賣唔到先係斷佢臂！<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多發展緊既盤，好似康城果邊，大部份佢都有份！<br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔好攪錯重點！"},{"pid":"c81df3371f9fc957424bf16ef8670e7663248cbe","tid":1553941,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:02:08.000Z","msg":"[急!!!]9/9有班中學生等緊你地救！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"975c66ece062979442a72c0b3f8e2b6109907c98","tid":1553941,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"總之有乜相關都搞掂佢啦"},{"pid":"eeed3c34c56ec1a091ef59e31f7b317ebf3c4e29","tid":1553941,"uid":80036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:23:49.000Z","msg":"要唔要喺佢賣樓抽籤前光復下佢？"},{"pid":"85d72b1ed664f2cb8d7441be279bb2fd8a1bd206","tid":1553941,"uid":209566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33788353744ffb0a55c10cdafa20dcdaac3cd238","tid":1553941,"uid":80036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeed3c34c56ec1a091ef59e31f7b317ebf3c4e29","tid":1553941,"uid":80036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:23:49.000Z","msg":"要唔要喺佢賣樓抽籤前光復下佢？"},"